gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 132, Warriors 122
gameRecap.excerpt: The Mavericks defeated the Warriors, 132-122. Luka Doncic totaled 39 points, eight rebounds, and 10 assists as Dante Exum added 19 points and five assists. Stephen Curry led the Warriors with 25 points and seven assists as Chris Paul added 24 points (six 3PT FG) and six assists. The Mavericks improve to 19-14 as the Warriors move to 15-17.
